revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

tpIpMRouteEnable.name: tpIpMRouteEnable
tpIpMRouteEnable.description: Select enable or disable to set the status of Multicast Forwarding in the router. The default is disable.

tpIpMRouteSGTable.name: tpIpMRouteSGTable
tpIpMRouteSGTable.description: The (conceptual) table containing multicast routing information for IP datagrams sent by particular sources to the IP multicast groups known to this router.

tpIpMRouteSGEntry.name: tpIpMRouteSGEntry
tpIpMRouteSGEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) containing the multicast routing information for IP datagrams from a particular source and addressed to a particular IP multicast group address.

tpIpMRouteSGSource.name: tpIpMRouteSGSource
tpIpMRouteSGSource.description: The IP address of the multicast packet source to be combined with the Group IP to fully identify a single route whose Mroute table entry.

tpIpMRouteSGIncomingInterface.name: tpIpMRouteSGIncomingInterface
tpIpMRouteSGIncomingInterface.description: The incoming interface on which multicast packets for this source /group arrive.

tpIpMRouteSGOutgoingInterface.name: tpIpMRouteSGOutgoingInterface
tpIpMRouteSGOutgoingInterface.description: The list of outgoing interfaces on which multicast packets for this source/group are forwarded.

tpIpMRouteSGRpfNeighbor.name: tpIpMRouteSGRpfNeighbor
tpIpMRouteSGRpfNeighbor.description: The address of the upstream neighbor (e.g., RPF neighbor) from which IP datagrams from these sources to this multicast address are received, or 0.0.0.0 if the upstream neighbor is unknown (e.g., in CBT).

tpIpMRouteSGUpTime.name: tpIpMRouteSGUpTime
tpIpMRouteSGUpTime.description: The time in seconds since the entry was created.

tpIpMRouteSGExpiryTime.name: tpIpMRouteSGExpiryTime
tpIpMRouteSGExpiryTime.description: The time in seconds before this entry will age out and be removed from the table.

tpIpMRouteSGProtocol.name: tpIpMRouteSGProtocol
tpIpMRouteSGProtocol.description: The multicast routing protocol which created this entry. The possibilities are: PIM-DM,PIM-SM.

tpIpMRouteSGFlags.name: tpIpMRouteSGFlags
